videos.headline: Georgia Southern takes quick lead with 1-yard TD
videos.description: Georgia Southern's Shai Wertz dives into the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Werts and Anderson give Georgia Southern a 14-0 lead with 58-yard TD
videos.description: Shai Wertz connects with Darion Anderson, who sprints into the end zone for a 58-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Fields strikes again with 25-yard TD run
videos.description: Georgia Southern's Wesley Fields increases the lead against South Alabama with a 25-yard touchdown run.
